entries.journal_entry_description: Working for the Hutt on Naboo.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Borvo wants his ex-partner retired, permanently. I should check where he was last spotted. He has a group of body guards with him I should watch out for.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: I've got to take out Montrus. He's likely to have some protection with him, but Montrus is my only concern.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Excellent! You've proven yourself again. I have something for you. Return to me and I'll give you something from my collection of valuable artifacts.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: I've killed Borvo's ex-business partner, now he wants to give me some kind of gift.
